subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: Mushers and their dogs took a leisurely jaunt through Anchorage in the ceremonial start of Alaska’s Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
